# Project Structure Rules

```
frontend/src/
├── pages/       # Route-level components (LandingPage.tsx, RequestPage.tsx, AuthPage.tsx, Contact.tsx)
├── components/  # Reusable components (NavBar.tsx, Footer.tsx, ContactInfo.tsx)
└── types/       # Shared TypeScript types (index.ts)
```

- Pages (route-level) → `frontend/src/pages/`
- Reusable UI → `frontend/src/components/`
- All types → `frontend/src/types/`
- Backend → `backend/` (FastAPI, Python, SQLModel)

## CSS Utility Classes (use these, don't reinvent)

- `.btn-hover-blue` — transition + primary-blue hover
- `.btn-hover-blue-secondary` — transition + tertiary-blue hover + pill shape
- `.btn-hover-shadow` — shadow on hover
- `.fade-in-up`, `.fade-in-up-delay-1/2/3` — staggered entrance animations

## Tailwind v4 Theme Tokens

- Colors: `bg-primary-blue` (#08b4fb), `bg-secondary-blue`, `bg-tertiary-blue` (#1e91c1), `bg-dark-blue` (#206988)
- Fonts: `font-primary` (Open Sans), `font-secondary` (Roboto), `font-quaternary` (Anton)
